OL,3,CNearly 1.5m households receive cold
OL,4,Cweather payments: Could you be
OL,5,Celigible?
OL,7,FCold weather payments have been paid
OL,8,Fto nearly 1.5 million households
OL,9,Facross England and Wales so far this
OL,10,Fwinter, the Government has said.
OL,12,FIt comes as the Met Office issues more
OL,13,Fweather warnings for rain and snow
OL,14,Famid falling temperatures.
OL,16,FThe #25 payments, known as cold
OL,17,Fweather payments, go to low-income
OL,18,Fhouseholds to help them with their
OL,19,Fbills.
