OL,3,CNearly 1.5m households receive cold
OL,4,Cweather payments: Could you be
OL,5,Celigible?
OL,7,FThe payments are made automatically
OL,8,Fwhen temperatures drop to 0 degrees
OL,9,Fcelsius or below for seven consecutive
OL,10,Fdays.
OL,12,FPeople receiving pension credit
OL,13,Fautomatically qualify for the
OL,14,Fpayments, but some households
OL,15,Freceiving other support, including
OL,16,Funiversal credit and income support,
OL,17,Fmay also be eligible if they meet
OL,18,Fadditional criteria.
