OL,3,CNearly 1.5m households receive cold
OL,4,Cweather payments: Could you be
OL,5,Celigible?
OL,7,FSecretary of State for Work and
OL,8,FPensions Pat McFadden said: "This
OL,9,Fsupport is a lifeline for vulnerable
OL,10,Fhouseholds when temperatures plummet."
OL,12,FPensioners on low incomes can apply
OL,13,Ffor pension credit, worth on average
OL,14,F#86 a week on average.
OL,16,FPension credit also acts as a gateway
OL,17,Fto accessing other support, including
OL,18,Fhelp with housing costs and free NHS
OL,19,Fdental treatment.
