OL,5,Celigible?
OL,7,FMorgan Vine, director of policy and
OL,8,Finfluencing at Independent Age said:
OL,9,F"With more than half of older people
OL,10,Fon low incomes across England and
OL,11,FWales regularly sharing that they are
OL,12,Fworried about meeting the cost of
OL,13,Ftheir heating bill, it is crucial that
OL,14,Fvital support like this reaches those
OL,15,Fwho need it most."
