OL,3,CNearly 1.5m households receive cold
OL,4,Cweather payments: Could you be
OL,5,Celigible?
OL,7,FYou do not need to apply for cold
OL,8,Fweather payments, if you are eligible
OL,9,Ffor them you should receive them
OL,10,Fautomatically. You can find out if
OL,11,Fthis applies to you on the government
OL,12,Fwebsite.
OL,14,FIn the case you are eligible, payments
OL,15,Fare made into the same bank or
OL,16,Fbuilding society account as your
OL,17,Fbenefit payments.
