OL,3,CNearly 1.5m households receive cold
OL,4,Cweather payments: Could you be
OL,5,Celigible?
OL,7,FHow much should I get and when?
OL,9,FYou should get #25 for each 7-day
OL,10,Fperiod of very cold weather between 1
OL,11,FNovember 2025 and 31 March 2026.
OL,12,FPayments come through within 14 days
OL,13,Fafter each period of very cold weather
OL,14,Fwhere you live.
OL,16,FIf you go into hospital this could
OL,17,Faffect your payment. The government
OL,18,Fadvises getting in touch with the
OL,19,FPension Service or Jobcentre Plus.
